title: How To Be Who You Really Claim To Be, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO299
itunes:title: How To Be Who You Really Claim To Be, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO299
description: What if you could retrain your thought process to actually go the extra mile to the point where even if you were sleeping, your dreams would be driven by a sub-conscious commitment to excellence? I’ve actually experienced that & you can too. While everybody else is conditioning their minds to do the least that is still acceptable...YOU can condition your mind to do the most to WIN. You can actually become the person you want everybody to believe you really are.
